snippet.title: The Valley of the Architects | Trailer 3 (RELEASE DATE)
snippet.description:
Trailer 3 for The Valley of the Architects. Releasing in 1 week (MAR 28, 2025)! Pre-Order now!

https://apps.apple.com/ca/app/the-valley-of-the-architects/id6740152476?platform=iphone

Follow architectural writer Liz as she journeys through Africa to uncover the secrets of the lost Architect. Use your wits to prevail against some of the most intriguing challenges you will ever face. Using only elevators, make your way through the trials and complete the tests the lost Architect left for you. Only with perseverance will you reveal the true story lying deep below.
